{"tid":1399280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【戰術討論】【知己知彼】【唔好硬碰】","createTime":"2019-08-03T06:08:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-03T06:15:52.000Z","uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"479e3936a4eb872d8359ce924865cd97c08e1545","tid":1399280,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:08:06.000Z","msg":"速龍小隊<br />\n人數：50至60人<br />\nReference: <a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20160209/54741305\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160209%2F54741305&d=MMgAXMBwwZFGDPTkcL6JsTsyqOHkMMjDRpVYVMaq87A%3D&h=d24551c5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20160209%2F54741305&h=6e7be522\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20160209/54741305</a><br />\n<br />\n防暴警察<br />\n人數：不詳<br />\nReference: 後補（有無人幫下手）<br />\n<br />\n＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝＝<br />\n尋晚瞓覺同周公呻，周公比左依啲以下建議我地...<br />\n<br />\n背景：話說今次會遍地開花，好幾個區都將會有示威<br />\n狗腦：其實如果各區都有衝擊發生既話，速龍、防暴根本無可能同時鎮壓各區，只可以集中兵力逐區擊破。<br />\n人腦：由於遍地開花，我地需要重組哨兵TG，即可化被動為主動。我地唔再需要等待到警犬進攻先再還拖博同情。警犬所作所為經已神人共憤。我地主動，警犬主力就要被牽制，同時間我地立即疏散休息食個下午茶先。然後就輪到下一個區。不停更替。"},{"pid":"98e08fab6cdd962ea5f504266eeab08aefe0c27b","tid":1399280,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:09:22.000Z","msg":"點睇"},{"pid":"7f81d48c72747e6ac8559a19febbf4eeccac7fb3","tid":1399280,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:10:33.000Z","msg":"由每區巴打組成，成本低"},{"pid":"da0c8f44ae3fea0e668432abf79f8b990d023279","tid":1399280,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7f81d48c72747e6ac8559a19febbf4eeccac7fb3","tid":1399280,"uid":158270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:10:33.000Z","msg":"由每區巴打組成，成本低"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-03T06:15:52.000Z","msg":"無錯